<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>로그인</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Charter:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/login.css">
</head>
<body>
    <main class="main-content">
        <div class="content-container">
            <div class="login-container">

                <h1 class="login-title">로그인 / 회원가입</h1>

                <p class="login-description">
                    처음 로그인 시 자동으로 회원으로 가입돼요.
                </p>

                <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
                    <div class="error-message">
                        <%= error %>
                    </div>
                <% } %>

                <a href="/api/auth/kakao" class="btn-kakao">
                    <span class="kakao-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path fill="#000000" d="M12 3C6.753 3 2.5 6.37 2.5 10.516c0 2.58 1.68 4.85 4.216 6.214-.15.54-.97 3.51-1.01 3.74 0 0-.02.17.09.23.11.06.24.02.24.02.32-.05 3.7-2.42 4.28-2.83.56.08 1.14.12 1.68.12 5.247 0 9.5-3.37 9.5-7.516C21.5 6.37 17.247 3 12 3z"/>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    카카오톡 계정으로 계속하기
                </a>

                <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 10px;">
                <a href="/" class="login-description">
                    메인 페이지로 돌아가기
                </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
